Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Tampakan Elementary School in the Municipality of Simunul, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Hadji Akbar Ulama Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 654
An Act Changing the Name of the Tampakan Elementary School in the Municipality of Simunul, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Hadji Akbar Ulama Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Tampakan Elementary School in the Municipality of Simunul, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is changed to Hadji Akbar Ulama Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
